    {
      "id": "dependency-web-service-stack",
      "name": "Web Service Stack Dependency Graph",
      "description": "A dependency graph captures which components a web service relies on to function: the load balancer depends on web/API servers, which depend on the auth service and application logic; the application in turn depends on a cache, primary database, and message queue, and queue workers depend on object storage, so a failure propagates up the chain.",
